Singer Simi has become the first Nigerian female artiste to reach 100mi streams on Audiomack. She was elated for the historical achievement on the popular global music streaming platform. The Duduke singer expressed gratitude for the honour, praising God and fans for the accomplishment. The mother of one tweeted: “@audiomackafrica thank you so much for the honour. First female to get 100 million plays on audiomack. I like it very much” she wrote.   Best Of Nollywood Awards to unveil host city for 14th…     AFRIMA mourns former Ghanaian DJ RAB Bakari     Sikiru Ayinde Barrister: K1 consolidates Fuji…   “Thank God for growth and thank my amazing fans for always supporting me.” Audiomack is a free global limitless music streaming and discovery platform that allows artistes to share their music and fans to discover new artistes, songs and albums.